-feather-3833076">比利·埃里什（Billie Eilish）的《羽毛鸟》（Birds of Feather of Feather of Feather）</a> ，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kelly-clarkson-perform-say-it-aint-so-with-weezer-3757532">Weezer</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kelly-clarkson-and-miranda-lambert-cover-chappell-roans-good-luck-babe-3796838">Chappell Roan</a>的曲目，Chappell Roan， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-kelly-clarkson-covering-the-last-dinner-partys-nothing-matters-3776455">最后一场晚餐派对</a>，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kelly-clarkson-cover-my-chemical-romances-welcome-to-the-black-parade-3093805">我的化学浪漫片</a>。它还诞生了克拉克森（Clarkson）在2022年的EP。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kelly-clarkson-says-she-has-lost-a-lot-as-she-marks-1000th-episode-of-chat-show-3848280">凯利·克拉克森（Kelly Clarkson）帖子说，她是第1,000集聊天节目，她“失去了很多”，</a>这是<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>首次出现的。</p> ;
